      • setIgnorePreferenceChanges

        public void setIgnorePreferenceChanges​(boolean ignore)
        For a bullseye, the changes to the global north reference and angular units are global which follows the behavior of the range and bearing arrow. A plugin might want to localize the north reference and angular units and not have it track changes global changes
        Parameters:
        ignore - true will ignore the global changes
